As expected, the TSVM performed better than the classic linear SVM, however
 due to the nature of the data, the classification performance difference
 between the two the TSVM and the SVM was not really substantial.
 Another thing to notice is that this example is somewhat counter-intuitive,
 because you could expect that for more training data available the difference
