 However the opposite happened, when more training data was available, the
 difference between their performance decreased.
 Another result of the experiment, that surprised us but we knew it could
 happen was the for the 100-200 setup the transductive parallel SVM had
 a little bit more classification performance than the non-parallel version.
 Even with this particularities in general terms the expected occurred,
